Toppings:

Little Caesars offers classic pizza toppings like:
pepperoni, Italian sausage, mushrooms, onions, green peppers, black olives, and pineapple, plus specialty options like their Old World Pepperoni and meats on their 5 Meat Feast™; you can also customize with extra cheese, jalapeños, and even bacon on sides like the Slices-N-Stix, offering a wide variety for build-your-own pizzas and signature recipes. 

Popular Toppings:
Meats: Pepperoni (including Old World), Italian Sausage, Ham, Bacon, Seasoned Beef.

Vegetables: Mushrooms, Onions, Green Peppers, Jalapeño Peppers, Black Olives, Pineapple.

Cheeses: Extra Cheese. 

Specialty Pizzas Featuring Toppings:

5 Meat Feast™: Bacon, Italian Sausage, Ham, Pepperoni, Seasoned Beef.
Ultimate Supreme: Pepperoni, Italian Sausage, Mushrooms, Onions, Green Peppers.
Hula Hawaiian®: Ham or Canadian Bacon and Pineapple. 

Customization Options:
You can often add toppings like pineapple, jalapeños, and black olives to your own creations, as well as select placement (whole or left/right) for some toppings. 
